<h1>Salesforce Authenticator setup</h1>

<% if current_user.phone.pairing_in_progress? %>

<p>It looks like you are in the middle of the pairing process. After accepting the connection request on your phone, refresh this page and you should be all set.</p>
<p>In case you did not receive the request or inadvertently rejected it, <%= link_to "click here", "/auth/phone", method: :delete %> to restart the process. Please <%= link_to "https://sfdc.co/pd-bread-comms", "contact" %> the BREAD team if the problem persists.</p>

<% elsif current_user.phone.paired? %>

<p>Your Canoe account is paired with your phone. New phone? <%= link_to "Delete the existing pairing", "/auth/phone", method: :delete %> and start over.</p>

<% else %>

<p>To pair your Canoe account with your phone, open the <a href="https://help.salesforce.com/articleView?id=salesforce_authenticator_overview.htm&type=0">Salesforce Authenticator app</a> then tap on <strong>New Account</strong> and enter the pairing phrase bellow:</p>

<%= form_tag "/auth/phone" do %>
<p>
<label>Two-Word Phrase</label>
<input name="pairing_phrase" autocomplete=off>
</p>
<p><input type=submit value="Pair phone"></p>
<% end %>

<% end %>
